         <div xml:id="abs" type="abstract" xml:lang="eng">
            <ab>In this document, sent from Sallyāna, Badarībāṇa Sāhī states that he has sent the
               Dasaĩ <foreign>prasāda</foreign> from various temples, some with delay.</ab>
         </div>

